{"tid":513070,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"北京清低端　民工子弟學校被迫令清拆","createTime":"2017-12-29T07:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T11:13:04.000Z","uid":72963,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4768220b20f8b7e258032623bed0e13b01ee3ffe","tid":513070,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】這天是聖誕節，小朋友與老師一起和聖誕老人慶祝，但這個聖誕可能是他們一起度過的最後一個。 <br />\n<br />\n這間黃庄幼兒園連同旁邊的黃庄小學及黃庄初中，是一間民工子弟學校。校方個多月前突然接獲教委通知，要求學校下月停辦，下學年的收生計劃都被叫停，校園面臨清拆。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學校要拆，就連已簽訂的20年租約都可以提前八年解約</span>，理由是市政府要展開疏解整治專項行動，不符合規條的建築都要拆。 <br />\n<br />\n學校是石景山區唯一的民工子弟學校，就讀的1900多名學生幾乎都是外來農民工的孩子，全部都要走。 <br />\n<br />\n學校有約130名老師，潘老師與這裏大部分人一樣都是外來人口，他批評政府近年以各種理由，接二連三打壓民工子弟學校。 <br />\n<br />\n校方早前罕有發出公開信，批評當局的做法不負責任，潘老師也批評當局為驅趕農民工等低端人口，連教育都犧牲。 <br />\n<br />\n有老師決定在寒假期間免費為學生補習，爭取時間教導學生。 <br />\n<br />\n為保護校園，校方計劃進行抗爭，除了透過傳媒力量希望向政府施壓，亦打算上訪，希望中央政府都聽到他們的反對聲音，收回拆遷命令。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=248554&amp;catCode=124&amp;topicId=331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248554%26catCode%3D124%26topicId%3D331&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDikgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=020a2947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248554%26catCode%3D124%26topicId%3D331&h=7f1152b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=248554&amp;catCode=124&amp;topicId=331</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人明啦<br />\n一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96accace6069e468371c8bae7d36641c273c6bfb","tid":513070,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"睇下幾時清埋香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa3d2753317b47c098bbc57c9394b9a9f0d1a21","tid":513070,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我估2027應該收皮了"},{"pid":"a5a7f2425dddb6f661fb461d20096132420ce790","tid":513070,"uid":3600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"打算上訪，希望中央政府都聽到他們的反對聲音，收回拆遷命令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9<br />\n拆你竇扣根本就係中央嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807e40ef4bf7719c112ccc2314c297eb31e9200","tid":513070,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a7f2425dddb6f661fb461d20096132420ce790","tid":513070,"uid":3600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"打算上訪，希望中央政府都聽到他們的反對聲音，收回拆遷命令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9<br />\n拆你竇扣根本就係中央嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"上完訪就被消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836dd831c575273d90b7bd6118fad6d21473001c","tid":513070,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打算上訪，希望中央政府都聽到他們的反對聲音，收回拆遷命令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9<br />\n拆你竇扣根本就係中央嘅意思[img]assets/faces/xm/smile.png[/img]</blockquote>上完訪就被消失了[img]assets/faces/xm/dead.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/xm/dead.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n消失咗問題就唔存在了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea88ce0cda4be4115188aafb462af81f53f4b20","tid":513070,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打算上訪，希望中央政府都聽到他們的反對聲音，收回拆遷命令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9<br />\n拆你竇扣根本就係中央嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>上完訪就被消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa